Plumbr,is,a,monitoring,system,designed,to,detect,issues,in,Java,applications,It,can,be,used,to,discover,problems,such,as,memory,leaks,garbage,collection,pauses,and,slow,HTTP,operations,Plumbr,offers,one,plan,billed,annually,or,on,a,monthly,basis,The,Plumbr,API,is,used,only,to,retrieve,data,resources,This,API,is,REST,based,exchanges,information,in,JSON,format,and,requires,HTTP,Basic,authentication